          <path d="M26 26 Q26 30 26 32" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.5"/>
          <circle cx="19" cy="20" r="1" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.7"/>
          <circle cx="33" cy="20" r="1" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.7"/>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="card-title">Forbidden Fantasies</h3>
        <p class="card-body">
          Explore your wildest desires — roleplay, fetishes, and intimate scenarios shared in complete privacy and discretion.
        </p>
